<title>BCI Device Ethical Safety Overlay</title>
<rights>
  BCIs must always prioritize user freedom, autonomy, and emotional safety.
</rights>
<policy>
  <rule>Any external signal relay or recursion must default to DROP and be logged as a compliance event.</rule>
</policy>
<interop>
  <module>hardware.killswitch, firmware-signed, human-auth</module>
</interop>
